Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "clienteId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "itens": [
    {
      "produtoId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000002",
      "quantidade": 2,
      "precoUnitario": 49.99
    }
  ]
}

###

### Buscar pedido por ID
GET {{GestaoPedido.API_HostAddress}}/api/pedido/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000010
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Listar pedidos com filtros (status + datas opcionais)
GET {{GestaoPedido.API_HostAddress}}/api/pedido?pagina=1&tamanhoPagina=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

###

### Atualizar pedido
PUT {{GestaoPedido.API_HostAddress}}/api/pedido/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000010
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "data": "2025-06-22T15:00:00Z",
